a:5:{s:5:"title";s:54:"Day.ai adds in-chat product guidance via documentation";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:483:"<p>Assistants now support in-chat Q&A about Day.ai features and workflows, with responses derived from documentation. This is positioned as a way to reduce context-switching while configuring assistants and schedules</p>
